📣🎊 G I V E A W A Y  A L E R T 🎊📣

#ad I like to think that I take enough precautions to stay #CyberSafe in general 😅👨🏻‍💻 I use 2FA when I can, always pick a unique password for all of my accounts and so. I also have been using @nortonsecurity's solutions to keep my PCs secure as well 👌🏻💯

However, no matter how cautious I can get, my personal data's safety is not always up to me 🙇🏻‍♂️ Our private data is usually at the mercy of the security measures from many of the online services we use on the daily 😅 

This brings us to one of my favorite features #Norton360 offers in its suite of Cyber Safety solutions. With its Dark Web Monitoring feature, I can stay up to date on the latest cyberattacks that involve my personal information, allowing me to be aware of potential phishing attacks and take precautions against them.

That being said, the awesome team at @nortonsecurity was kind enough to provide me 3 discount codes for Norton 360 with LifeLock, valued at $150 for me to giveaway 🎉🎊 So if you want to be one of the 3 winners, make sure to

Follow @araltasher && @nortonsecurity 🔥
Comment what kind of PC you are currently using 💻

The winners will be announced next week Wednesday, July 21st 12PM EST
Giveaway is for US Only and you must be 18+ to enter.

node.text:
Hope you all had a great, relaxing weekend 🔋😃 As some of you know, as a recent #SamsungPartner , I've had the chance to use the #GalaxyBookPro360 laptop from @SamsungMobileUSA as my productivity device in the past month 👨🏻‍💻💯

So after spending a decent amount of time trying it out in my daily workflow, I wanted to circle back and give a more in-depth feedback from my experience 🤙🏻 

Starting off with the build quality; the Galaxy Book Pro 360 is an incredibly slim and light device, and yet, it still has a solid feel in hand. My biggest fear was the durability of the hinge mechanism, but switching between laptop and tablet modes feels very secure. And I've certainly been enjoying the flexibility.

The Super AMOLED Touch Display is another feature that impressed me right away and continued to deliver throughout my experience using it! The colors are very vibrant, which makes consuming content as much fun as creating 👌🏻 

And speaking of creative workflow, the S-Pen has been clutch in editing all my recent posts. Especially when doing some detailed dodge & burn edits on my shots 🤩💯 And I love the fact that I can just use the same pen interchangeably on all my Galaxy products, so I don't have to carry a separate S-Pen for my tablet 😅 

All in all, I am very happy with the Galaxy Book Pro 360 throughout my testing. It's quickly become my go-to device for on-the-go workflow 👌🏻💯 What are your thoughts? Do you have any additional questions? Let me know down in the comments section 👇🏻👇🏻 ​​​​​
